        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 6 at 2:04PM MDT until June 6 at 2:30PM MDT by NWS Grand Junction CO</headline>
        <description>SVRGJT

The National Weather Service in Grand Junction has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northwestern Mesa County in west central Colorado...
Western Garfield County in west central Colorado...
Northeastern Grand County in east central Utah...

* Until 230 PM MDT.

* At 203 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 26 miles northwest
of Fruita moving east at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
northwestern Mesa, western Garfield and northeastern Grand
Counties.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
